Localization.Name: Palatino Backpack Mark I
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Heavy Backpack
Carrying Capacity: 180K µSCU
Core Compatibility: Heavy

Elegant design meets innovation with the Palatino armor from Quirinus Tech. The associated backpack seamlessly integrates into the armor, matching its silhouette while also providing ample storage. The Mark I variant is primarily icy white with blue and red highlights.
